description.narrative: Emergency-affected children, women and families have access to life-saving and life-sustaining interventions in line with the CCCs, which contributes to Sanitation, Water. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2015, the most vulnerable girls and boys have sustainable and equitable access to and use quality, targeted basic social services, particularly to accelerate progress toward MDGs 1, 2, 3, 4
